  "text": "Based on KEGG database, the screened DEGs in the two groups were gathered in eight categories, including total network, metabolic process, genetic information transfer, environmental information transfer, intracellular biological process, biological systems, human disease and drug development [CITATION_1] . The enriched pathways were calculated by Fisher's exact test with the criteria of FDR <0.05.",
